。其核心优势在于打破传统教育的时空限制，通过互动化、游戏化的学习模式增强公众防灾意识，助力社区、学校及企事业单位构建科学防灾体系。</span></p>\"}]','0:0:0:0:0:0:0:1','','福建省','厦门市','MSEdge','Windows'),(1900463493289005058,'2025-03-14 16:26:20',2,'ES同步','GET','/course/admin/course/es','','0:0:0:0:0:0:0:1','','福建省','厦门市','MSEdge','Windows'),(1900463634913873921,'2025-03-14 16:26:54',2,'排序','PUT','/course/admin/course/sort','[[{\"id\":1900434105084362754,\"sort\":1}]]','0:0:0:0:0:0:0:1','','福建省','厦门市','MSEdge','Windows'),(1900463646762782722,'2025-03-14 16:26:56',2,'排序','PUT','/course/admin/course/sort','[[{\"id\":1900434105084362754,\"sort\":1}]]','0:0:0:0:0:0:0:1','','福建省','厦门市','MSEdge','Windows'),(1900463818578251777,'2025-03-14 16:27:37',2,'站点友情链接修改','PUT','/system/admin/website/link/edit','[{\"id\":1790569180659134465,\"statusId\":1,\"sort\":1,\"linkName\":\"常见自然灾害类型与特\",\"linkUrl\":\"https://www.baidu.com/\",\"linkTarget\":1}]','0:0:0:0:0:0:0:1','','福建省','厦门市','MSEdge','Windows'),(1900463878829428738,'2025-03-14 16:27:52',2,'ES同步','GET','/course/admin/course/es','','0:0:0:0:0:0:0:1','','福建省','厦门市','MSEdge','Windows'),(1900463968646254594,'2025-03-14 16:28:13',2,'分类删除','DELETE','/course/admin/category/delete','[1248248345805754369]','0:0:0:0:0:0:0:1','','福建省','厦门市','MSEdge','Windows'),(1900464050263216130,'2025-03-14 16:28:33',2,'专区修改','PUT','/course/admin/zone/edit','[{\"id\":1060472271471714305,\"statusId\":1,\"sort\":1,\"zoneName\":\"常见自然灾害类型与特征\",\"zoneDesc\":\"常见自然灾害类型与特征\"}]','0:0:0:0:0:0:0:1','','福建省','厦门市','MSEdge','Windows'),(1900464074376269826,'2025-03-14 16:28:38',2,'专区课程添加','POST','/course/admin/zone/course/save','[{\"sort\":1,\"courseId\":1900434105084362754}]','0:0:0:0:0:0:0:1','','福建省','厦门市','MSEdge','Windows'),(1900464164679634946,'2025-03-14 16:29:00',2,'专区课程添加','POST','/course/admin/zone/course/save','[{\"sort\":1,\"courseId\":1900434105084362754}]','0:0:0:0:0:0:0:1','','福建省','厦门市','MSEdge','Windows'),(1900464322897170434,'2025-03-14 16:29:38',2,'专区修改','PUT','/course/admin/zone/edit','[{\"id\":106047227147171